subSubSection.paragraph:
Description of female from Skeleton Gorge, South Africa .
Length, 3.3 mm , greatest width, 1.65 mm . Trunk (
Fig. 2
) with 23 segments (all other females in collection with 21 or 22 segments). Other nonsexual characters as in male. Coxae of second legpair enlarged, extended posteriomesally. Cyphopods mesal to coxae, evidently with mesal valves only, lacking lateral valves and opercula; mesal valves with pair of setae (
Fig. 11
).
